3 (15) Local governments or associations of local governments may contract with a
4 person, firm, or company to perform the plans and specifications inspection or
5 building inspection functions required of the local government by the provisions of
6 this section if:
7 (a) The person performing the plans and specifications inspection is certified by
8 the department as having successfully completed the test requirements
