1 1. Footings;
2 2. Foundations;
3 3. Concrete slabs;
4 4. Framing;
5 5. Electrical;
6 6. Plumbing;
7 7. Heating;
8 8. Ventilation; and
9 9. Air conditioning.
10 (b) Any plan review or inspection conducted by a qualifying third-party
11 inspector shall be at least as extensive as a plan review or inspection that
